bin

Class AppState

  • java.lang.Object
    • bin.AppState

  • public class AppState
extends java.lang.Object
    Control Class. Background state in parallel with the front GUI. Keep temporary information to be used in front GUI. Front GUI can only access this class, can not modify this class.
